Show HN: Caroot – The AI assistant helps you resolve your daily repetitive tasks
text:
Caroot is an AI assistant that helps independent workers maximize their productivity. We’re an all-in-one solution for managing, requesting tasks and streamlining communication. With a focus on simplicity and efficiency, our app helps you easily save your workload and get more done in less time.

1. Easily manage all your tasks in one place Stay organized and on your to-do list with our easy-to-use task management system. You can create and prioritize tasks, set deadlines, and track progress.

2. Make a request; our professional workers will resolve it for you Streamline the process of receiving, managing, and delivering your task orders. You can easily communicate with the assignee, set up payment options, and manage delivery details in one place.

3. Talk with Harper about anything you don’t know how to do Our Harper could help you with general information questions. With the chatbot handling routine inquiries, you can focus on more important tasks.

It’s free! So download and give it a go.
